/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the cityscape. The street, lined with lush green trees, stretches out into the distance, flanked by towering buildings on either side. The sky above is a clear blue, adding a serene backdrop to the urban landscape. The image is taken from a low angle, emphasizing the height of the buildings and the expanse of the sky. The predominant colors in the image are green, blue, and gray, reflecting the natural and man-made elements of the scene.
